UID:Greater_Orlando_Volleyball_Club-Summer_Bash_Coed_Tournament_(B/BB)-202
 6-07-25T09:00:00
DESCRIPTION:Summer Bash Tournament Details\n\nTournament Details\n\n- Date
 : July 25\, 2026\n- Time: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM  - One division tournament 
 goes from 9am to 6pm \n- Two division tournament will be split 9am - 6pm 
 and 12pm - 9pm\n\n- Location: Dover Shores Community Center\n- 8 Player Ma
 x Roster\n- Iron Middles Allowed\nTRUE COED FORMAT - 3 Men + 3 Women on th
 e court at all times\nCome hang & have a good day\n\n- Free entry for anyo
 ne to come watch\n- Snacks and drinks provided for everyone \n- Lunch pro
 vided for players\nEntry & Prizes\n\n- $250 registration per team \n- $50
 0 cash prize for winner (subject to change with registration numbers) \n-
  Individual awards for group stage\n- Finals MVP award\nHow to Register\n\
 n- Team captains sign up your full team to secure your spot.\n- Spots are 
 limited and will fill quickly.\n\nSummer 2026\n\nMore info: https://goadul
 tsportsleague.leagueapps.com/app/tournaments/5018478
LOCATION:Dover Shores Community Center
URL:https://goadultsportsleague.leagueapps.com/app/tournaments/5018478
