DESCRIPTION:Summer Bash Tournament Details\n\nTournament Details\n\n- Date
 : July 25\, 2026\n- Time: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM \n- Location: Dover Shores 
 Community Center\n- 9 Player Max Roster\n- No Iron Middles \n- 4 Matches 
 Guaranteed (Best of 3)\n\nCome hang & have a good day\n\n- Free entry for 
 anyone to come watch\n- Snacks and drinks provided for everyone \n- Lunch
  provided for players\n\nEntry & Prizes\n\n- $350 registration per team | 
 $100 donated directly to causes\n- $500 cash prize for winner (subject to 
