BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:[Greater Orlando Volleyball Club] Saturday Indoor Volleyball Leagu
 e - Summer
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260613T170000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260613T210000
UID:Greater_Orlando_Volleyball_Club-Saturday_Indoor_Volleyball_League_-_Su
 mmer-2026-06-13T17:00:00
DESCRIPTION:Welcome to Greater Orlando Volleyball’s Summer Indoor League
 \n\nWe’re back for another season of indoor league play at Dover Shores 
 — built for intermediate+ players who want real competition with that so
 cial GOVB energy.\n\nLeague Format - 6v6 teams (coed optional)\n- Rosters:
  7–9 players (we recommend 8)\n- Two matches per week\; best of three\n-
  Sets played to 25\, 25\, 15  (50-minute matches)\n- USAV rules with refs
  (teams provide officials)\nPrice - $60 early bird\, $70 regular\, $80 lat
 e\n- Payment plans available\nLeague Perks - League t-shirt (Week 2/3\, sp
 onsorship dependent)\n- Championship shirts + medals\n- End of season part
 y \nSeason Schedule - June 13 — Open Gym + Team Practice\n- June 20 - W
 eek 1\n- Championship Week: August 15th\n- June: 13\, 20\, 27\n- July: 11\
 , 18\, 25\n- August: 1\, 8\, 15\nDivisions - One coed division\n- Men’s 
 height net\n- Intermediate level required\nFree Agents Sign up solo and we
 ’ll place you on a team. If we can’t\, you’ll get a full refund.\n\n
 Subs - Outside subs: must be invited + pay single-day fee\n- League player
 s can sub freely\n- No subs on Championship Week\nSee you on the court.\nG
 reater Orlando Volleyball\n\nSummer 2026\n\nMore info: https://goadultspor
 tsleague.leagueapps.com/leagues/volleyball-(indoor)/4968685-saturday-indoo
 r-volleyball-league---summer
LOCATION:Dover Shores Community Center
URL:https://goadultsportsleague.leagueapps.com/leagues/volleyball-(indoor)
 /4968685-saturday-indoor-volleyball-league---summer
END:VEVENT
