BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:[Greater Orlando Volleyball Club] Queens of the Court
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260919T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260919T170000
UID:Greater_Orlando_Volleyball_Club-Queens_of_the_Court-2026-09-19T09:00:0
 0
DESCRIPTION:Queens of the Court\nLadies\, you asked for it — it's back. 
 Queens of the Court is Greater Orlando Volleyball's next women's tournamen
 t\, one full Saturday of volleyball built entirely around you. Real divisi
 ons\, real competition\, and a gym full of women who play the way you do. 
 Grab your team and come take the crown.\n\nTournament Details\n- Date: Sat
 urday\, September 19\, 2026\n- Time: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM\n- Location: Dove
 r Shores Community Center\n- 8 Player Max Roster\n- Iron Middles Allowed\n
 \nTournament Format\n- 6 women on the court at all times\n- Pool play into
  single elimination\n- Teams self-ref through bracket play\; semifinals an
 d finals are officiated\n- Format depends on final team count — we'll co
 nfirm the schedule once registration closes\nEntry & Prizes\n- $250 regist
 ration per team\n- Entry covers champion prizes\, event shirts\, snacks an
 d drinks\, and player lunch\n- Register by September 5 to guarantee your e
 vent shirt\n- Individual awards for group stage\n- Finals MVP award\n- Reg
 istrations support GOVB's adult volleyball programming across Orlando — 
 we're a 501(c)(3) nonprofit\n\nCome hang & have a good day\n- Free entry f
 or anyone to come watch\n- Snacks and drinks provided for everyone\n- Lunc
 h provided for players\n\nDon't have a team yet?\nCome to Women's Open Gym
  on Sundays in August — August 2\, 9\, 16\, and 23. That's where teams g
 et built. Show up\, play\, find your six\, and register before spots fill.
 \n\nHow to Register\n- Team captains sign up your full team to secure your
  spot.\n- Register by September 5 to guarantee shirts for your roster.\n- 
 Spots are limited and will fill quickly.\n\nMore info: https://goadultspor
 tsleague.leagueapps.com/app/tournaments/5093604
LOCATION:Dover Shores Community Center
URL:https://goadultsportsleague.leagueapps.com/app/tournaments/5093604
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:[Greater Orlando Volleyball Club] Saturday Indoor Volleyball Leagu
 e - Fall '26
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260905T170000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260905T210000
UID:Greater_Orlando_Volleyball_Club-Saturday_Indoor_Volleyball_League_-_Fa
 ll_'26-2026-09-05T17:00:00
DESCRIPTION:Welcome to Greater Orlando Volleyball’s Fall Indoor League\n
 \nWe’re back for another season of indoor league play at Dover Shores 
 — built for intermediate+ players who want real competition with that so
 cial GOVB energy.\n\nLeague Format - 6v6 teams (coed optional)\n- Rosters:
  7+\, no cap  (we recommend 8)\n- At least four sets each week\n- Sets pl
 ayed to 21\, 21\, 15  (50-minute matches)\n- USAV rules with refs (teams 
