 ayed to 21\, 21\, 15  (50-minute matches)\n- USAV rules with refs (teams 
 provide officials)\nPrice - $70 early bird\, $75 regular\, $80 late\n- Pay
 ment plans available\nLeague Perks - League t-shirt (Week 2/3\, sponsorshi
 p dependent)\n- Championship shirts + medals\n- End of season party \nSea
 son Schedule - September 5  — Open Gym + Team Practice\n- September 12
   - Week 1\n- November 21 - Championship Week\n- September:  5\, 12\, 19
 \, 26\n- October: 3\, 10\, 17\, 24\n- November:  14\, 21\nDivisions - One
  coed division\n- Men’s height net\n- Intermediate level required\nFree 
 Agents We suggest that those interested in playing without a team come to 
 the Open Gym + Team Practice session. Our league generally fills up quickl
 y and we rarely has a full spot for free agent teams. \n\nWe also have op
 en gyms in August that would also be a great place to make friends and bui
 ld teams. You can find those sessions here: https://goadultsportsleague.l
 eagueapps.com/classes/5064743-open-gym---summer-series\n\nSubs - Outside s
 ubs: must be invited + pay single-day fee\n- League players can sub freely
 \n- No subs on Championship Week\nSee you on the court.\nGreater Orlando V
 olleyball\n\nSummer 2026\n\nMore info: https://goadultsportsleague.leaguea
 pps.com/leagues/volleyball-(indoor)/5094328-saturday-indoor-volleyball-lea
 gue---fall-26
